@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ccxwpg(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (tmp / wp.cos(0.99))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v0 + 0.36 - v1 + 0.38)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp((v0 + 0.01 * v2 + 0.69)))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.exp(0.99))
    data[tid] = v0
